AGRICULTURE CODE

Medical Examiners and who is only using a restricted-use or statelimited-use pesticide or a regulated herbicide as a drug or
medication during the course of the veterinarian's normal practice or
as a private applicator may not be required to obtain a license under
this chapter to purchase or use the restricted-use or state-limiteduse pesticide or regulated herbicide.
Added by Acts 1997, 75th Leg., ch. 1369, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1997.

